  "texts": [
    "Another drawback mentioned was that certain tasks may not align well with the use of GeoGebra.",
    "Moreover, students who receive feedback solely from GeoGebra may adopt a broad perspective without engaging in reasoning.",
    "This could potentially result in students easily accepting the general validity of a conjecture through continuous dynamic transformations of geometry objects in the software application.",
    "The primary objective of this study is to provide a comprehensive analysis of the landscape of GeoGebra research within the field of mathematics education from 2007 to 2023.",
    "This entails monitoring and documenting publication trends over time, identifying and categorizing major thematic clusters through visual analytics with VOSviewer, and examining the productivity and influence of individual authors, countries, and institutions."
  ]
